{"type":"message","id":"d463a262","parentId":"17c3c745","timestamp":"2026-05-30T10:45:07.847Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have detailed content from the two most relevant summaries. Let me also check the other two summaries to understand the full picture.\n\nFrom sum_bac1212a13950d64 (2026-05-19), the content shows:\n- 2026-05-11: First successful write to Feishu Bitable with record_id `recvj7mDkqG8rj` ✅\n- The Bitable tool (feishu_bitable) was initially not available in the tool list\n- There was a permission issue (1254302) that required adding the bot as a collaborator\n- Eventually the write succeeded on 2026-05-11\n\n\n- The table structure shows fields like `文本`, `单选`, `日期`, `附件` for tracking product details including name, price in local currency, growth rate, monthly sales, profit margin, estimated profit, 1688 comparable links, category, site, recommendation level, collection status, IP risk, and action suggestions\n\nFrom sum_cec73caa8f09fbad (2026-05-24), I'm seeing an attempted batch write of 10 records to the Feishu Bitable that failed completely.\n\nThe batch_create operation returned a validation error about missing table_id, but when I tested with a single record create, it actually succeeded and returned record_id \"recvkuOJRqFJcH\". So the issue isn't that writes fail entirely—it's specifically the batch operation that has a problem with the table_id parameter, possibly in how it's positioned in the request structure. There's also something going on with the date format that I need to look into.\n\nLooking at what the user actually reported, they said \"飞书没有记录\" which means \"no records in Feishu.\" From the historical data, writes did succeed at various points—on 2026-05-11 and again on 2026-05-19—so the question is whether records actually exist in the system right now, or if something happened to delete or clear them. I should check sum_afb31b7e39dbe833 to get more context about what the user is actually experiencing.\n","thinkingSignature":"e73131513e89a04bd64c68f043cb383362c0865091752f0a72c2a29fb448f272"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pfvmsldw5l0t_1","name":"lcm_describe","arguments":{"allConversations":true,"id":"sum_afb31b7e39dbe833"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pfvmsldw5l0t_2","name":"lcm_describe","arguments":{"allConversations":true,"id":"sum_bf7ad3df10fee02c"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":7159,"output":539,"cacheRead":37479,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45177,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780137894738,"responseId":"0669f2a7a534be0a58c26420bcfdde88"}}
{"type":"message","id":"77862d3d","parentId":"d463a262","timestamp":"2026-05-30T10:45:07.882Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_pfvmsldw5l0t_1","toolName":"lcm_describe","content":[{"type":"text","text":"LCM_SUMMARY sum_afb31b7e39dbe833\nmeta conv=218 kind=leaf depth=0 tok=808 descTok=0 srcTok=18333 desc=0 range=2026-05-24 09:03 GMT+8..2026-05-24 09:07 GMT+8 budgetCap=4000\nmanifest\nd0 sum_afb31b7e39dbe833 k=leaf tok=808 descTok=0 srcTok=18333 desc=0 child=0 range=2026-05-24 09:03 GMT+8..2026-05-24 09:07 GMT+8 cost[s=808,m=19141] budget[s=in,m=over]\ncontent\n轨道2选品流程 - Hair Claws类目进展\n\n关键发现：\n认证问题已解决：MCP key因shell自动截断显示为***…qt09导致认证失败。解决方法是将完整key写入/tmp/sorftime_key.txt后读取。\n\n成功获取数据：\n1. similar_product_feature分析（17个产品样本）- 核心产品特征（按月销量占比排序）：\n   - 强握力/牢固抓握: 100%产品强调\n   - 防滑设计: 92.31%/94.58%\n   - 适合所有发质: 92.31%/93.72%\n   - 轻便: 84.62%/87.14%\n   - 舒适贴合: 76.92%/79.21%\n   - 耐用: 76.92%/78.45%\n   - 磨砂/亮面: 69.23%/71.83%\n   - 多功能: 69.23%/70.56%\n   - 环保材料: 38.46%/39.12%\n   - 多种颜色: 69.23%/68.91%\n   - 套装形式(2-12件): 61.54%/62.34%\n   - 旅行便携: 53.85%/55.21%\n   - 无压痕: 46.15%/47.38%\n   - 金属材质: 38.46%/39.87%\n   - 礼盒包装: 38.46%/39.54%\n   - 大尺寸(4.3寸): 30.77%/31.23%\n\n2. category_report Top100数据已获取（部分产品）：\n   - B0BVXBCQNJ Kitsch Octopus大号（排名#6）- 月销26,061/$234,288/评分9,010/4.30星\n   - B09GYPGLZZ Kitsch Mini小号（排名#1）- 月销19,548/$156,189/评分3,413/4.60星\n   - B0DX8FDJBD Kitsch Small Flat（排名#3）- 月销15,047/$120,226/评分2,254/4.20星\n   - B09Z7L79K6 LuSeren 4.3寸大号（排名#4）- 月销14,508/$110,116/评分14,830/4.70星\n   - B0DQDP625C SMKSL 12件套装（排名#2）- 月销13,504/$103,171/评分1,302/4.70星\n   - B0CBWGMSL4 Sisiaipu彩色12件（排名#5）- 月销11,788/评分3,714/4.70星\n\n问题：\n- product_report返回的是使用方法文本而非实际数据（可能该工具仅返回指引）\n- Python解析category_report失败（JSON解析错误，需处理响应格式）\n\n当前时间：2026-05-24 09:07 GMT+8\n下一步：重新获取完整Top100数据并解析，下一步应尝试直接解析JSON或使用product_detail获取单品详情，飞书写入待后续执行\n\nFiles: none\nExpand for details about: keyword_list returned top US keywords like \"summer dresses for women 2026\", \"eggs\" (not hair claws specific), product_report tool usage instructions, full Top100 product list (129KB+ truncated output), complete similar_product_feature JSON with 20 feature rows, complete category_report JSON structure."}],"details":{"id":"sum_afb31b7e39dbe833","type":"summary","summary":{"conversationId":218,"kind":"leaf","depth":0,"tokenCount":808,"descendantCount":0,"descendantTokenCount":0,"sourceMessageTokenCount":18333,"fileIds":["file_cf95aa5ed3ec4c13"],"parentIds":[],"childIds":[],"messageIds":[6018,6019,6020,6021,6022,6023,6024,6025,6026,6027,6028,6029,6030,6031,6032,6033,6034,6035,6036,6037,6038,6039,6040,6041,6042,6043,6044,6045,6046,6047,6048,6049,6050],"earliestAt":"2026-05-24T01:03:58.000Z","latestAt":"2026-05-24T01:07:13.000Z","createdAt":"2026-05-24T01:25:58.000Z"},"manifest":{"tokenCap":4000,"budgetSource":"delegated_grant_remaining","nodes":[{"summaryId":"sum_afb31b7e39dbe833","parentSummaryId":null,"depthFromRoot":0,"depth":0,"kind":"leaf","tokenCount":808,"descendantCount":0,"descendantTokenCount":0,"sourceMessageTokenCount":18333,"childCount":0,"earliestAt":"2026-05-24T01:03:58.000Z","latestAt":"2026-05-24T01:07:13.000Z","path":"","costs":{"summariesOnly":808,"withMessages":19141},"budgetFit":{"summariesOnly":true,"withMessages":false}}]}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780137907877}}
{"type":"message","id":"f631e05c","parentId":"77862d3d","timestamp":"2026-05-30T10:45:07.888Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_pfvmsldw5l0t_2","toolName":"lcm_describe","content":[{"type":"text","text":"LCM_SUMMARY sum_bf7ad3df10fee02c\nmeta conv=218 kind=leaf depth=0 tok=1129 descTok=0 srcTok=14413 desc=0 range=2026-05-24 09:00 GMT+8..2026-05-24 09:02 GMT+8 budgetCap=4000\nmanifest\nd0 sum_bf7ad3df10fee02c k=leaf tok=1129 descTok=0 srcTok=14413 desc=0 child=0 range=2026-05-24 09:00 GMT+8..2026-05-24 09:02 GMT+8 cost[s=1129,m=15542] budget[s=in,m=over]\ncontent\nTikTok Shop 东南亚发饰选品每日自动执行流程\n触发时间：每日 09:00 AM Asia/Shanghai\n执行内容：1. 调用 Sorftime API 获取 Amazon Hair Claws 类目数据 2. 按 SOP v5.2 筛选评分 3. 将结果写入飞书多维表 4. 发送选品报告\n\nSOP 版本：v5.2（2026-05-20 更新）\n核心策略更新：「跟品为主 + 套装/组合扩展」\n核心变更：新增入场时间窗口7项过滤器作为所有轨道的统一前置标准，不通过直接淘汰，不进入后续评分流程\n\n入场时间窗口7项过滤器（统一前置，所有轨道适用）：\n1. 上架时间 ≤30天\n2. 近7天销量增长率 ≥50%\n3. 总销量 100-500单\n4. 评价数 50-200条\n5. 同款卖家数量 ≤20个\n6. 客单价 3-10美元\n7. 退货率 ≤10%\n\n三轨选品策略：\n轨道1：Sorftime-TK数据 → VN站类目数据\n轨道2：Sorftime-亚马逊数据 → 美区 Hair Claws 类目（月销量≥1000，上架≥6个月）\n轨道3：Sorftime-1688数据 → 1688货源\n\n飞书多维表配置（写入目标）：\nURL: https://bytedance.feishu.cn/base/AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd\napp_token: AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd\ntable_id: tblHU2do30jzinJT\n视图配置：全部商品（默认）、S级推荐、高利润商品（≥50%）、高增长商品（增长率≥30%）、待审核\n\nSorftime API Key：rhblyi90suxqqwfnnwzwy2tdvuhwqt09（2026-05-20 更新）\n\n每日选品目标：10条候选品入库\n筛选标准：综合评分≥100分 + 增长率>0 + 毛利率≥30%\n选品来源标注：区分 Sorftime-TK数据 / Sorftime-亚马逊数据 / Sorftime-1688数据\n\n成本模型（越南站）：\n平台成本：41% + ¥2\n毛利达标线：单品≥30%，套装≥45%\n否决线：毛利润率 <20% 直接放逐\n\n关键文件路径：\nSOP本地：/home/halei/workspace-tts/docs/SOP.md\nMEMORY：/home/halei/workspace-tts/MEMORY.md\n飞书SOP文档：https://www.feishu.cn/docx/Q9NGdkdnio7YAmx2Ok7ccHc3nbb\n\n已知用户偏好：\n- 以跟品为主，爆什么跟什么，不需要复杂的三步验证\n- 差异化手段：套装组合、变体扩展\n- 保守测算：无自然流量假设，盈利才能做\n\n工作流程时间线：\n09:00 自动跑 Sorftime VN 站类目数据 → 综合评分排序 Top10\n09:00-09:45 参数卡死 → 三步验证 → 延展选品 → 评分 → 利润测算\n10:00 写入飞书多维表格（10条）+ 飞书通知推送\n人工时段 审核推荐结果、确认采购、下单征集\n\nFiles: none\nExpand for details about: full SOP scoring matrix (170分8维度), complete three-step verification method, 备货黄金法则详解, 节日布局时间表, IP侵权黑名单完整内容, variant expansion strategy specifics, Amazon product selection parameters from config/mcporter.json, 每日选品日志文件内容, 三步快速验证详细操作步骤."}],"details":{"id":"sum_bf7ad3df10fee02c","type":"summary","summary":{"conversationId":218,"kind":"leaf","depth":0,"tokenCount":1129,"descendantCount":0,"descendantTokenCount":0,"sourceMessageTokenCount":14413,"fileIds":[],"parentIds":[],"childIds":[],"messageIds":[5993,5994,5995,5996,5997,5998,5999,6000,6001,6002,6003],"earliestAt":"2026-05-24T01:00:05.000Z","latestAt":"2026-05-24T01:02:51.000Z","createdAt":"2026-05-24T01:25:14.000Z"},"manifest":{"tokenCap":4000,"budgetSource":"delegated_grant_remaining","nodes":[{"summaryId":"sum_bf7ad3df10fee02c","parentSummaryId":null,"depthFromRoot":0,"depth":0,"kind":"leaf","tokenCount":1129,"descendantCount":0,"descendantTokenCount":0,"sourceMessageTokenCount":14413,"childCount":0,"earliestAt":"2026-05-24T01:00:05.000Z","latestAt":"2026-05-24T01:02:51.000Z","path":"","costs":{"summariesOnly":1129,"withMessages":15542},"budgetFit":{"summariesOnly":true,"withMessages":false}}]}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780137907883}}
{"type":"message","id":"3c68c2ed","parentId":"f631e05c","timestamp":"2026-05-30T10:45:27.946Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have good context. Let me synthesize:\n\n1. The \"飞书没有记录\" - from the context, this likely refers to records not being written to the Feishu Bitable. The user is asking about this situation.\n\n2. The most recent operations involving writing to Feishu Bitable:\n   - 2026-05-24: There was a batch_write failure for 10 records (sum_cec73caa8f09fbad). The error was \"table_id: must have required properties table_id\" for batch_create. Single record create worked.\n   - 2026-05-20: A cron job was supposed to run at 9AM and write to the Bitable at 10AM (sum_bf7ad3df10fee02c)\n   - 2026-05-19: There were successful test writes (sum_bac1212a13950d64 shows a test write succeeded)\n   - 2026-05-24:轨道2 Hair Claws选品 - batch_create failed, but single record worked\n\n3. The Feishu Bitable:\n   - app_token: AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd\n   - table_id: tblHU2do30jzinJT\n\n4. The core issue: The batch_create operation was failing with a validation error on the table_id parameter, though individual record creation worked fine. The user is reporting that records aren't appearing in their Feishu Bitable, which could mean the cron job on 2026-05-24 didn't complete successfully or the batch_write operation failed and never retried.\n\nThe user's complaint about missing records likely stems from either the cron job not executing that morning, or the failed batch operation leaving the database incomplete. Looking at the 2026-05-24 conversation, I had the data ready but the batch_create call failed, so the records never made it into the system. The root cause appears to be a parameter format issue with the table_id field that's preventing batch operations from succeeding.\n","thinkingSignature":"e70a9a4aa77a8bb9c0ab99ad07670e2eaf05feabebcf6df1babea6148e7eb9c2"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n```json\n{\n  \"answer\": \"「飞书没有记录」指的是选品记录未能写入飞书多维表格（Bitable）的场景。\\n\\n**最近写入飞书多维表的操作及结果：**\\n\\n1. **2026-05-24（今天）轨道2 Hair Claws选品** — batch_create批量写入失败，10条记录全部报错：\\n   - `batch_create`报错：`\\\"table_id: must have required properties table_id\\\"`（Validation failed）\\n   - 单条`create`测试成功，写入1条测试记录（record_id: `recvkuOJRqFJcH`）\\n   - 原因：batch_create的table_id参数格式或位置有问题；字段格式需调整（如商品名称需纯文本、选品来源需字符串数组而非对象数组）\\n   - 状态：**待修复，数据未能写入**\\n\\n2. **2026-05-19 早晨** — 选品测试写入**成功**（record_id: `recvj7mDkqG8rj`），验证了飞书多维表格写入流程可行\\n\\n3. **2026-05-24 9AM cron任务** — 触发轨道2选品流程（Hair Claws类目），按SOP v5.2筛选→评分，但写入步骤因batch_create失败而卡住\\n\\n**飞书多维表配置（已知）：**\\n- app_token: `AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd`\\n- table_id: `tblHU2do30jzinJT`\\n- 表名：「选品库」\\n\\n**结论：** 「飞书没有记录」是真实情况——今天（2026-05-24）轨道2筛选出的10条Hair Claws候选品**全部未能写入**多维表，因为batch_create批量写入接口有参数格式问题。单条写入可以工作，但完整流程卡在批量写入环节。修复方向：调整batch_create的table_id参数位置，或改用逐条create循环写入。\",\n  \"citedIds\": [\"sum_cec73caa8f09fbad\", \"sum_bac1212a13950d64\", \"sum_afb31b7e39dbe833\", \"sum_bf7ad3df10fee02c\"],\n  \"expandedSummaryCount\": 4,\n  \"totalSourceTokens\": 425 + 5523 + 808 + 1129,\n  \"truncated\": false\n}\n```"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4160,"output":970,"cacheRead":42447,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47577,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780137907924,"responseId":"0669f2b49202f08cd8c05e83dd3c1d75"}}
